name: Call Synapse pipeline with a notebook activity
description:
Use this template to call a Synapse pipeline with a notebook activity.

In the template, we use a Web activity to call a Synapse pipeline with a notebook activity, do A Web activity to get Synapse pipeline status, Until web activity returns status of Succeeded, Failed, or Canceled. A Fail activity fails the pipeline and customizes both error message and error code when pipeline run fails.
